---
title: Jerk Chicken & Caribbean Coconut Sauce with Roast Pumpkin Veggie Medley
description: With hints of pimento, pepper and nutmeg, our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning is perfect for jazzing up juicy chicken breast. We've even sprinkled some in the creamy coconut sauce for a meal that's sure to be a success.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
